            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/rd22/" class=" " title="呼叫的石头">呼叫的石头</a>
                (Maranatha)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33921927">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">忽视了上帝（真理真相善意公义怜悯）的眼睛，人就追逐在同类严重的表现，即形式化的表演，同类的点头。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-01-06 15:45</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
